overview:
Impressive Invitations constant focus is delivering outstanding, high quality invitations along with exceptional customer service. At Impressive Invitations we know how busy life can get, that’s why we want to provide you with the most efficient service the industry has to offer. Quick, easy and stress free is the key! Our promise to you is a 2 day production turnaround, express post standard for all orders and to top it all off a 100% unconditional guarantee – every customer is happy or we will give you your money back!

Browse through unique invitations and greeting cards when you shop at Impressive Invitations online. With customisation of the invitation word, look and feel, and other value added services, this online shop offers you a great service. We also offer wide range of birthday invitations, first birthday invitations, party invitations, Birth Announcement cards, christmas cards, christening invitations, corporate invitations, party invitations, Bridal Shower Invitations and hens night invitations.
